  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1042020/extras/53a1b7eb3c41a10b7ea3e64d1e624f84.avif?t=1749388783\" width=576 height=324 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forced to work on a passenger ship as a servant, Eris finds herself praying for a way out of her situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When one fateful day, she finds her prayers answered, the results are not what she bargained for. The ship is unexpectedly struck by a powerful storm, causing it capsize.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The next thing she knows, she awakes on a mysterious island. What brought her here, and for what purpose? Eris must begin exploring the island to find out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic turn-based RPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a mysterious island</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle monster to become stronger</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather seeds to power up</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1042020/extras/53a1b7eb3c41a10b7ea3e64d1e624f84.avif?t=1749388783\" width=576 height=324 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forced to work on a passenger ship as a servant, Eris finds herself praying for a way out of her situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When one fateful day, she finds her prayers answered, the results are not what she bargained for. The ship is unexpectedly struck by a powerful storm, causing it capsize.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The next thing she knows, she awakes on a mysterious island. What brought her here, and for what purpose? Eris must begin exploring the island to find out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic turn-based RPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a mysterious island</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle monster to become stronger</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather seeds to power up</p></li></ul>",
